Package agent

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    This class is used to describe the actions an Agent can take.
    ActionResult
    This class is used to describe the action results that an action can have.
    Agent
    This class described the agent whom will plan and solve the problem in order to achieve his desire.
    AgentMessage
    This class is used for communication between two agents.
    Belief
    This class holds the Belief of the agent.
    Desire
    This class represents the Desire of the agent which is to get the highest score.
    Intention
    This class holds the Intention of the agent or in other words his short term goal for the completion of his final Intention (to get the highest score).
